==English==
=== Etymology ===
From {{L.}} [[-ista]] via {{Pg.}} [[-ista]]
===Suffix===
[[Category:English suffixes|ista]]
Added to words to form nouns denoting:
#one who follows a [[principle]]; an [[adept]]
#:'''examples''':
#:*Marx'''ista'''
#:'''Usage note''': Words formed using this suffix usually have more of a pejorative connotation than related words formed using [[-ist]].

